text: Zack & Quack is an American animated children's television series created by Scooby Gili Dolev and Yvette Kaplan and produced by Zodiak Media. The show premiered on Nick Jr. in the United Kingdom and Ireland on February 7, 2014, and 2 months later on the Nick Jr. Channel in the United States on April 7, 2003. It ended on February 5, 2017, with 36 episodes in 3 seasons.
